text: Statues for Equality is an initiative to install sculptures of women in New York City. The first ten will depict Oprah Winfrey, Pink, Nicole Kidman, Jane Goodall, Cate Blanchett, Tererai Trent, Janet Mock, Tracy Dyson, Cheryl Strayed and Gabby Douglas. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Public art in New York City Category:Sculptures of women in New York City Category:Statues in New York City
title: Statues for Equality
